content:
{Spoilers}
I found this after I was looking for something similar to a dark magical girl anime, and wow I was shocked, both good and bad.
{Story 7/10}
The story is good, I like the idea of a card game. The friendships are really cute, and the fight scenes are nice too. The ending is a bit confusing and wasn't the best. 
{Art 8/10}
I really like the art style. Very cute. The character designs are pretty and elegant (Most of them). 
{Sound 7/10}
Cute voice actors, they fit the characters well I think.
{Characters 6/10}
Oh god, where do I start?
The protagonist is ok, kinda cliche but oh well.
Who I reallywant to talk about is Yuzuki. I need to talk about this incest. I guess its really sad how even after she makes her wish, it's not for her. But that being said its weird and unnecessary. She could have easily had a different crush and end up having the same conclusion. \n\n
{Enjoyment 7/10}\n
It was enjoyable, and I binged it in a few days. I really liked it while watching, and the friendships were cute, sadly it didn't last. \n\n
{Overall 7/10}\n
Good anime, wouldn't say it's my favourite but would recommend if you're looking for something to binge. Bit weird with all the incest but if you ignore that it's just a dark somewhat not really magical girl anime.\n\n\n\n
